### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "nickname": "testuser",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 로그인 (쿠키에 JWT 저장됨)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "testuser",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 프로필 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/users/profile

### 프로필 수정
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "updatedUser"
}

### 비밀번호 변경
PUT http://localhost:3000/users/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword456@"
}

### 재로그인 (쿠키에 JWT 저장됨)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "updatedUser",
  "password": "NewPassword456@"
}

###

### 게시글 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/articles

### 게시글 등록
POST http://localhost:3000/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "첫 번째 게시글",
  "content": "테스트 게시글입니다."
}

### 게시글 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/articles/1

### 게시글 수정
PATCH http://localhost:3000/articles/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수정된 게시글",
  "content": "수정된 내용입니다."
}

### 게시글 좋아요 (토글)
POST http://localhost:3000/articles/1/like

### 게시글 상세 조회 (isLiked, likeCount 확인)
GET http://localhost:3000/articles/1

### 내가 좋아요한 게시글 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/users/likes/articles

### 게시글 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:3000/articles/5

---

### 상품 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### 상품 등록
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "테스트 상품",
  "description": "이것은 테스트 상품입니다.",
  "price": 19900
}

### 내가 등록한 상품 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/users/products

### 상품 상세 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1

### 상품 수정
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "수정된 상품명",
  "description": "설명을 수정했습니다.",
  "price": 29900
}

### 상품 좋아요 (토글)
POST http://localhost:3000/products/1/like

### 상품 상세 조회 (isLiked, likeCount 확인)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1

### 내가 좋아요한 상품 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/users/likes/products

### 상품 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/3

---

### 로그아웃
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout

### 토큰 재발급
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh

### 회원 탈퇴
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/delete
